1) To Run all the test methods in one time
command = py.test

2) To run particular input test file
command = py.test test_demo1.py

3) To run only selected test method
command = py.test -k login -v

4) To run a group of tests using markers
command  =  py.test -m login
command =  py.test /Pytest/test_demo1.py -m login

5) To run the tests in parallel mode install the below package.
command = pip install pytest-xdist

  To run the tests in parallel use below command:
  command  = py.test /Pytest/test_Webpage_Login.py -n 5

6) To install pytest html reports, install below package
command = pip install pytest-html

7) To get html reports for running tests use below command to run the tests
command = pytest .\Pytest\test_Google_test.py -v -s --html=test_google_report.html
command = pytest .\Pytest\test_google_fixture.py -v -s --html=test_google_fixture_report.html